<http://example.org/medical-devices-ontology#SafetyAlert> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A corrective action consisting of a safety alert"@en .
<http://example.org/medical-devices-ontology#SafetyAlert> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Safety Alert"@en .
# 
# http://example.org/medical-devices-ontology#Severity
<http://example.org/medical-devices-ontology#Severity> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
