<http://example.org/medical-devices-ontology#Severity> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Severity"@en .
# 
# http://example.org/medical-devices-ontology#UserNotice
<http://example.org/medical-devices-ontology#UserNotice> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
